@page "/"
@using Sidio.Sitemap.Blazor
@* default *@
@attribute [Sitemap]

<PageTitle>Website Analyzer</PageTitle>

<div style="max-width:1000px;">
<RadzenText TextStyle="TextStyle.H1" class="mb-4">
    Website Analyzer
</RadzenText>

<RadzenText class="mb-6">
    Your website's performance directly impacts user experience and search engine rankings. 
    Our specialized tools help you identify and fix common issues that could be holding your site back.
</RadzenText>

<RadzenRow class="rz-mt-6">
    <RadzenColumn>
        <RadzenCard class="p-6" Style="height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between;">
            <RadzenText TextStyle="TextStyle.H3">Broken Link Checker</RadzenText>
            <RadzenText class="mb-4">
                Dead links frustrate users and harm your SEO. Our broken link checker crawls
                your entire website, identifying broken internal and external links that need
                attention. Stay on top of your site's health with comprehensive link analysis.
            </RadzenText>
            <a href="/broken-link-checker">
                <RadzenButton Text="Find Broken Links" ButtonStyle="ButtonStyle.Primary"/>
            </a>
        </RadzenCard>
    </RadzenColumn>
    <RadzenColumn>
        <RadzenCard class="p-6">
            <RadzenText TextStyle="TextStyle.H3">Cache Warmer</RadzenText>
            <RadzenText class="mb-4">
                Don't let slow page loads drive visitors away. Our cache warming tool
                proactively loads your pages into server cache, ensuring consistently fast
                response times across your entire site. Perfect for after deployments or
                before high-traffic periods.
            </RadzenText>
            <a href="/cache-warmer">
                <RadzenButton Text="Warm Your Cache" ButtonStyle="ButtonStyle.Primary"/>
            </a>
        </RadzenCard>
    </RadzenColumn>
</RadzenRow>    

<RadzenText TextStyle="TextStyle.H2" class="mb-4 rz-mt-6">Why Use Website Analyzer?</RadzenText>

<RadzenText class="mb-2">
    Whether you're managing a small business website or a large e-commerce platform, 
    maintaining optimal performance is crucial. Our tools help you:
</RadzenText>

<ul class="mb-6">
    <li>Identify and fix broken links before they impact your users</li>
    <li>Ensure consistently fast page loads with intelligent cache warming</li>
    <li>Monitor your website's health with detailed historical data</li>
    <li>Automate maintenance tasks to save time and resources</li>
</ul>

<RadzenText>
    Get started now with our free tools, or create an account to unlock advanced features 
    like scheduling, historical tracking, and detailed performance analytics.
</RadzenText>
</div>